snippet.title: Disney Dreamlight Valley - Dapper Delights Update Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/disney-dreamlight-valley/

Tiana from Disney's The Princess and the Frog joins the Valley! Help Tiana set up her restaurant and a new Stall, explore culinary traditions with Remy, and plan a New-Orleans-style parade with your Disney and Pixar friends.

Bring some Roaring Twenties style 'n' swing with the "Dapper Delights" Star Path, which includes new flapper-inspired fashions and furniture, a dapper new look for Donald Duck, and more!

#ps5 #ps5gmaes #ps4 #ps4games #disneydreamlightvalley
